{"tid":1368794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元天屯人士聽住，聽日有個重要任務。","createTime":"2019-07-26T14:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T15:02:08.000Z","uid":62011,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0c50461fc234f6af14135b2baf10fe3112d7fe04","tid":1368794,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"我係唔同FB見到元朗拆巴士牌，sell Hong Kong 商場入面又遮住車站指示牌。<br />\n<strong>我絕對有理由相信今次黑勢力會混入人群，然後帶住一班係市區入嚟，唔識元朗地形既人入村，然後畀村民誤會入嚟有人搞事，到時引發民眾爭執，黑警得米。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以熟悉元朗地形既元天屯朋友，靠你哋幫手。如果你見到一班人往村方向行，<strong>無論佢哋係咪自己友，請截住佢哋，瞭解清楚。</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，想請元天村圍村朋友，原居民。遊行人士唔入村其實已經係共識，如果你見到一班人入，但係唔係自己村既人請你阻止佢哋入去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n萬分感謝。"},{"pid":"11d3dc642c62373ec8a97053ce83f61cce218bc2","tid":1368794,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:31:45.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"909155fe3f4d0647ee3505cae995b120fe4d5c3e","tid":1368794,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:33:43.000Z","msg":"喺最外圍嘅巴絲打可以叫啲人行入中間<br />\n唔比佢地出手 自律維持秩序<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713169abe5c3e1eea681ec853fc9b03d888d1d26","tid":1368794,"uid":62011,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:34:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遊行人士唔入村係共識 勿中港共計</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6804d3a41c3c976080bc21c38ca73ae5882ce47f","tid":1368794,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4c77607c7ee0106c4075f7854b5a14f7fc082c1a","tid":1368794,"uid":285195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:38:32.000Z","msg":"thanks! push"},{"pid":"0744557175bba8baa5317b3342afb9524b225754","tid":1368794,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"首先唔入村未必真係共識<br />\n我就一定不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但我認同元天屯居民有見及此<br />\n問一聲總沒有壞<br />\n擔任埋導遊就仲好添</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"68cc916cd1549a5151df700ae50cd552832218e4","tid":1368794,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0744557175bba8baa5317b3342afb9524b225754","tid":1368794,"uid":267007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:39:53.000Z","msg":"首先唔入村未必真係共識<br />\n我就一定不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但我認同元天屯居民有見及此<br />\n問一聲總沒有壞<br />\n擔任埋導遊就仲好添</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:41:16.000Z","msg":"我意思係有需要的話可以擔任埋導遊<br />\n相信好多人真心未必踏足過元朗"},{"pid":"29234a33d2a980362f0e35c9f93daa306dcacd15","tid":1368794,"uid":263699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千其唔好被人帶風向！</span></span>"},{"pid":"1daea72b1553013bb180c2b2adc473e7dc24c782","tid":1368794,"uid":19728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T15:02:08.000Z","msg":"元朗市區界線：<br />\n如果以元朗大馬路出發<br />\n向北過左西鐵路軌 (不過安寧路同郎屏西鐵站中間有大橋村)<br />\n向西過左水邊村遊樂場(差館個十字路口)/體育路/元朗大球場/元朗劇院<br />\n向南過左馬田路/馬棠路 (元朗劇院/元朗消防局/大棠路油站/陳震夏中學)<br />\n向東過左元朗西鐵站/雞地(基元/基朗中學)<br />\n<br />\n行過左呢啲地標就要小心入左村<br />\n<br />\n利申：外國巴打 以前元朗讀中學 聽日唔會去"}]}